Inductive nsearch_spec_result (goal : Int) (work : nf_list) (ds : disjs) (ni : nested_imps) (ai : atomic_imps) (a : atoms) (context : flist) : Set := NSearch_Res : forall ni1 : nested_imps, le_ni ni1 ni -> deco_sound work ds ni1 ai a -> nsearch_spec_result_aux goal work ds ni1 ai a context -> nsearch_spec_result goal work ds ni ai a context.

Definition nsearch_spec (goal : Int) (work : nf_list) (ds : disjs) (ni : nested_imps) (ai : atomic_imps) (a : atoms) (context : flist) := deco_sound work ds ni ai a -> nsound work ds ni ai a context -> nminimal work ds ni ai a context -> nsearch_spec_result goal work ds ni ai a context.
